rollers\nand up to 34 switches, so to tolerate up to 5 unique Byzantine and additional 5\navailability-induced controller failures (a total of 10 unique controller\nfailures). We quantify and highlight the dynamic decrease in the packet and CPU\nload and the response time after each successful failure detection.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Feb 2019 10:42:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-08"}
